panels.name: Events by Top 25 Buckets
panels.queryString:
$$cloudTrail AwsApiCall
| json "eventSource"
| where eventSource = "s3.amazonaws.com"
| json "eventType"
| where eventType = "AwsApiCall"
| json "eventName"
| json "requestParameters.bucketName" as bucketName
| count by bucketName, eventName
| topk(25, bucketName) by eventName
| fields -_rank
| transpose row bucketName column eventName

panels.name: Calls by Event Over Time
panels.queryString:
$$cloudTrail AwsApiCall
| json "eventSource"
| where eventSource = "s3.amazonaws.com"
| json "eventType"
| where eventType = "AwsApiCall"
| json "eventName"
| json "requestParameters.bucketName" as bucketName
| timeslice 1m
| count by _timeslice, eventName
| transpose row _timeslice column eventName

panels.name: Top 25 Resources
panels.queryString:
$$cloudTrail AwsApiCall
| json "eventSource"
| where eventSource = "s3.amazonaws.com"
| json "eventType"
| where eventType = "AwsApiCall"
| json "sourceIPAddress"
| json "requestParameters.key" as resource
| json "requestParameters.bucketName" as bucketName
| count as calls by bucketName, resource
| sort calls
| limit 25

panels.name: Top IP Public Addresses Over Time
panels.queryString:
$$cloudTrail AwsApiCall
| json "eventSource"
| where eventSource = "s3.amazonaws.com"
| json "eventType"
| where eventType = "AwsApiCall"
| json "requestParameters.bucketName" as bucketName
| json "sourceIPAddress"
| json "eventName"
| where sourceIPAddress matches /\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+/
| where isPublicIP(sourceIPAddress)
| timeslice 1m
| count as events by _timeslice, sourceIPAddress
| topk(10, sourceIPAddress) by _timeslice
| fields -_rank
| transpose row _timeslice column sourceIPAddress

panels.name: Top 10 Users
panels.queryString:
$$cloudTrail AwsApiCall
| json "eventSource"
| where eventSource = "s3.amazonaws.com"
| json "eventType"
| where eventType = "AwsApiCall"
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.sessionContext.sessionIssuer.userName" as userName
| json "requestParameters.bucketName" as bucketName
| json "sourceIPAddress"
| json "eventName"
| timeslice 1m
| count as events by userName
| sort events
| limit 10

panels.name: Top 25 Error Messages
panels.queryString:
$$cloudTrail AwsApiCall error
| json "eventSource"
| where eventSource = "s3.amazonaws.com"
| json "eventType"
| where eventType = "AwsApiCall"
| json "requestParameters.bucketName" as bucketName
| json "eventName"
| json "errorCode" as errorCode
| json "errorMessage" as errorMessage
| count as errors by bucketName, errorCode, errorMessage
| sort errors
| limit 25

panels.name: Location of API Calls
panels.queryString:
$$cloudTrail AwsApiCall
| json "eventSource"
| where eventSource = "s3.amazonaws.com"
| json "eventType"
| where eventType = "AwsApiCall"
| json "sourceIPAddress"
| where sourceIPAddress matches /\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+/
| where isPublicIP(sourceIPAddress)
| json "requestParameters.bucketName" as bucketName
| json "eventName"
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code from geo://location on ip = sourceIPAddress
| count as events by sourceIPAddress, latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code
| sort events

panels.name: API Calls
panels.queryString:
$$cloudTrail AwsApiCall
| json "eventSource"
| where eventSource = "s3.amazonaws.com"
| json "eventType"
| where eventType = "AwsApiCall"
| json "requestParameters.bucketName" as bucketName
| json "sourceIPAddress"
| json "eventName"
| count as events

panels.name: Buckets Accessed
panels.queryString:
$$cloudTrail AwsApiCall
| json "eventSource"
| where eventSource = "s3.amazonaws.com"
| json "eventType"
| where eventType = "AwsApiCall"
| json "eventName"
| json "requestParameters.bucketName" as bucketName
| count as requests by bucketName
| sort requests
| limit 25

panels.name: Outliers on API Calls
panels.queryString:
$$cloudTrail AwsApiCall
| json "eventSource"
| where eventSource = "s3.amazonaws.com"
| json "eventType"
| where eventType = "AwsApiCall"
| json "requestParameters.bucketName" as bucketName
| json "sourceIPAddress"
| json "eventName"
| timeslice 1m
| count as events by _timeslice
| outlier events
